---

This project wraps and rebrands GSD Core (https://github.com/open-gsd/gsd-core),
which is MIT-licensed by OpenGSD. Spec-Horus is not affiliated with OpenGSD.

The convertContent/hermes.js, codex.js, copilot.js, gemini.js, claude.js
modules in bin/lib/content-converters/ are derived from
`gsd-core/bin/install.js` (specifically the
`convertClaudeTo[Runtime]Markdown` and `convertClaudeCommandTo[Runtime]Skill`
functions) and the `convertContentToHyphen` helper from
`gsd-core/scripts/fix-slash-commands.cjs`. They are reimplemented in plain
Node.js (CommonJS) for spec-horus; the original is MIT-licensed by
OpenGSD.
